latestPosts.caption:
The masterminds behind Kota Factory, Panchayat, Aspirants…. (the list goes on and on…) and then there’s me! 🥰
Feeling super grateful to be in the company of these legendary creators.. and for their belief in me. When storytellers of this calibre choose you for a role so far from who you are — one that shatters every box you’ve ever been put in — it feels like a quiet victory. A win not loud with applause, but deep with meaning. To be seen, stretched, and trusted… @arunabhkumar @deepakmishra18 @theviralfever ❤️

THANK YOU guys for loving and resonating with Gram Chikitsalay ❤️ I’m on top of the moon 🙏🏼❤️

Shoutout to our amazing writers @vaibhavsuman @shreyasrivastava10 and the man behind it all - our director #RahulPandey 💕
